        {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": {
                "paragraph_content": [
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": "Problem 4 Given a set of column vectors "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "y _ { 1 } , \\ldots , y _ { n } \\in \\mathbb { R } ^ { m }"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": ", let "
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "equation_inline",
                        "content": "\\mathcal { V } = \\operatorname { s p a n } \\{ y _ { 1 } , . . . , y _ { n } \\} \\subset \\mathbb { R } ^ { m }"
                    },
                    {
                        "type": "text",
                        "content": ". How can we find "
